videos.headline: Delpit's sack thwarts Clemson's opening drive
videos.description: LSU safety Grant Delpit bursts through the line and sacks Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence to force the punt on the opening drive.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Delpit's sack thwarts Clemson's opening drive) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Higgins' blindside block pushes back Galloway's big reception
videos.description: Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence finds Braden Galloway for 42 yards, but Tee Higgins gets hit with an illegal block penalty pushing the Tigers back a little.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Higgins' blindside block pushes back Galloway's big reception) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow's Houdini act negated by illegal man downfield
videos.description: LSU's big gain on a Joe Burrow completion to Thaddeus Moss is brought back on an ineligible man downfield.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow's Houdini act negated by illegal man downfield) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence blows kiss to crowd on rush TD
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence fakes LSU's defense and keeps it himself on a one-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Lawrence blows kiss to crowd on rush TD) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow finds Chase in stride for 52-yard TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow sends the ball downfield to Ja'Marr Chase, who makes the catch and walks into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow finds Chase in stride for 52-yard TD) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Higgins trucks defender on Clemson trick-play TD
videos.description: Tee Higgins plows through a LSU defender on a reverse en route to a Clemson 36-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Higgins trucks defender on Clemson trick-play TD) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow caps off big pass with TD run
videos.description: Joe Burrow connects with Ja'Marr Chase for 56 yards to set LSU up inside the five-yard line. A few plays later, Burrow keeps it himself for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow caps off big pass with TD run) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jefferson's filthy juke has Clemson defender moonwalking
videos.description: Joe Burrow slips a pass to Justin Jefferson, who speeds up the sideline and fools a Clemson defender to the turf.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jefferson's filthy juke has Clemson defender moonwalking) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow delivers perfect TD to Chase
videos.description: Joe Burrow puts the ball exactly where it needs to be as Ja'Marr Chase makes the grab in the end zone for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow delivers perfect TD to Chase) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Randy Moss' son snags TD before halftime
videos.description: Joe Burrow takes a shot on a six-yard touchdown to Thaddeus Moss, who is the son of NFL legend Randy Moss.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Randy Moss' son snags TD before halftime) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence starts off hot, Burrow answers back
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence jump-starts Clemson early, but Joe Burrow answers back as the first half goes on as LSU holds a lead going into halftime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Lawrence starts off hot, Burrow answers back) 2020/01/13 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Etienne pushes forward for TD, Clemson tacks on two-point conversion
videos.description: Travis Etienne muscles across the goal line for a touchdown and then Trevor Lawrence finds Amari Rodgers for the two-point conversion.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Etienne pushes forward for TD, Clemson tacks on two-point conversion) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Clemson's Skalski ejected for targeting
videos.description: James Skalski lays a hit on Justin Jefferson, and after review, the Clemson linebacker is tossed for targeting.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson's Skalski ejected for targeting) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moss' TD catch makes dad happy
videos.description: Joe Burrow finds Thaddeus Moss for a short touchdown and Moss' dad, Randy, couldn't be happier as he cheers from the stands.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Moss' TD catch makes dad happy) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Marshall climbs ladder to haul in Burrow's fifth TD pass
videos.description: Joe Burrow's fifth touchdown pass of the game is on the money to Terrace Marshall Jr. for a 24-yard LSU score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Marshall climbs ladder to haul in Burrow's 5th TD pass) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Chase gets to his feet like a boss
videos.description: After Joe Burrow's pass to Ja'Marr Chase falls incomplete, Chase shows off his strength as he flips to his feet while laying on the ground.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chase gets to his feet like a boss) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dabo won't let Lawrence get down after costly fumble
videos.description: Dabo Swinney tries to lift the spirits of Trevor Lawrence after coughing up a fumble late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dabo won't let Lawrence get down after costly fumble) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow's parents elated as LSU seals CFP victory
videos.description: Joe Burrow connects with Clyde Edwards-Helaire for a game-sealing first down and Burrow's parents embrace with happiness in the stands.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burrow's parents elated as LSU seals CFP victory) 2020/01/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow, Lawrence embrace as LSU claims throne
videos.description: Joe Burrow and Trevor Lawrence share a moment as purple and gold confetti falls on Mercedes-Benz Stadium.

videos.headline: Burrow: LSU was fitted for rings before game
videos.description: Joe Burrow reflects on LSU's victory over Clemson and speaks on the inspiration drawn from his father.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Burrow: LSU was fitted for rings before game) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lawrence throws for 234 and rushes for a TD in championship loss
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence struggles to get into a rhythm as he throws for 234 yards and rushes for one touchdown in Clemson's loss to LSU.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Lawrence throws for 234 and rushes for a TD in championship loss) 2020/01/13 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Burrow caps perfect season with 6 TDs
videos.description: Heisman winner Joe Burrow throws five touchdowns and runs in another to lead undefeated LSU to a CFP National Championship win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow caps perfect season with 6 TDs) 2020/1/14 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Burrow's six-TD performance leads LSU to national title
videos.description: Joe Burrow outduels Trevor Lawrence as he passes for 463 yards and five touchdowns while adding another TD on the ground to lead LSU to a 42-25 defeat of Clemson in the College Football Playoff National Championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Burrow’s six-TD performance leads LSU to national title) 2020/01/13 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Coach O, Burrow hoist championship trophy in NOLA
videos.description: Ed Orgeron and Joe Burrow accept The College Football Playoff National Championship Trophy following their victory over Clemson.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Misc. (Coach O, Burrow hoist championship trophy in NOLA) 2020/1/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Palmer: Bengals should sign contract for Burrow immediately
videos.description: Jesse Palmer makes a case why Joe Burrow's CFP performance should prompt the Bengals to select him with the No. 1 pick in the NFL draft.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Palmer: Bengals should sign contract for Burrow immediately) 2020/01/13

videos.headline: Dabo: The better team won Monday
videos.description: Dabo Swinney says he's grateful for his team and how hard his players fought, but the better team won Monday in LSU.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Dabo: The better team won tonight) 2020/01/13

videos.headline: Lawrence on CFP loss: 'Just wasn't my night'
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence explains what went wrong for himself and the Clemson Tigers in their loss to LSU and reflects on the great things the team has accomplished so far.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Lawrence on CFP loss: ‘Just wasn’t my night’) 2020/01/13

videos.headline: Coach O's celebratory meal: A ham sandwich
videos.description: Ed Orgeron says his victory meal after LSU's National Championship win vs. Clemson will be a ham sandwich.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Coach O’s celebratory meal: A ham sandwich) 2020/1/13 SVP

videos.headline: Orlovsky: Burrow had the best season I've ever seen
videos.description: Dan Orlovsky credits Joe Burrow for having the best season he's ever seen from a quarterback, and says he called his shot and "Babe Ruth-ed" the national championship.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Orlovsky: Burrow had the best season I've ever seen) 2020/01/14 ESHEET Get Up

videos.headline: Stephen A. silenced by Clemson losing to LSU
videos.description: Stephen A. Smith apologizes to Ryan Clark and Marcus Spears for not believing that LSU could beat Clemson.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Stephen A. silenced by Clemson losing to LSU) 2020/01/14 ESHEET FT
